This application lets you modify an image with different modifiers:
How to use:
1. Open the "File" menu and open an image on your device with "Open" or create a new with the "New Image" option
2. Open the "Modify" menu and select a modifier, some will create a new window with either a ColorSelector or a Slider
3. Undo your changes by either removing all modifiers with the "No Modifier" option or go back step by step by pressing "CTRL+Z" on your keyboard. You can also use "CTRL+Y" to redo.
4. Select "Save" in the "File" menu to browse directories to save your modified image.